<p align="left"><b>

<font SIZE="3">The Polissoir<br>

</font></b><br>
<font style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 400">Copyright 
2013. This article originally appeared in the
<a target="_blank" href="../0_incl/FineToolJourn-track.asp">Fine Tool Journal</a></font></p>
</td>
<td align="right" width="101" height="26" valign="bottom">
<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight:700">
<a href="../cSchwarz-index.asp">
<img border="0" src="../../00-000-globIncl/intNavImg/arrowBack.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a> 
1 of 4 <a href="Polissoir-02.asp">
<img border="0" src="../../00-000-globIncl/intNavImg/arrowNext.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a></span></td>
<td align="right" width="14" height="26" valign="bottom">
